#    THEN the changed category is saved


Scenario Outline: Copy Document Category
    GIVEN a document category exists
    WHEN Administrator copies this category
    THEN the category is copied


Scenario: Delete Document Category
    GIVEN a document category exists
    WHEN Administrator deletes this category
    THEN the category is deleted
